min":false},"created_at":"2015-04-09T12:50:05Z","updated_at":"2015-04-09T12:50:05Z","body":"Sorry yes, this is of course possible. Here's a fully working core file with the values used from my app.\n![2015-04-09 14_49_19-tdrawabletest](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/4849383/7066961/afd7c8fa-dec7-11e4-8242-e3390bed3bf4.png)\n\nBlue line indicates the desired width. The TiledDrawable exceeds that width.\n\n``` Java\npackage com.mk1x86.G3DViewer;\n\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.ApplicationAdapter;\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.Gdx;\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.Color;\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.GL20;\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.Pixmap;\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.Pixmap.Format;\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.Texture;\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.g2d.SpriteBatch;\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.g2d.TextureRegion;\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.scenes.scene2d.utils.TextureRegionDrawable;\nimport com.badlogic.gdx.scenes.scene2d.utils.TiledDrawable;\n\npublic class TDrawableTest extends ApplicationAdapter {\n    private TiledDrawable tiledDrawable;\n    private TextureRegionDrawable regionDrawable;\n    private Texture texture;\n    private SpriteBatch batch;\n    public TDrawableTest() {\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void create () {\n        // create simple texture\n        Pixmap p = new Pixmap(155,10, Format.RGB888);\n        p.setColor(Color.GRAY);\n        p.fill();\n        p.setColor(Color.BLUE);\n        p.drawLine(0, 0, 0, 9);\n        p.setColor(Color.RED);\n        p.drawLine(154, 0, 154, 9);\n        texture = new Texture(p);\n        p.dispose();\n\n        tiledDrawable = new TiledDrawable(new TextureRegion(texture));\n\n        regionDrawable = new TextureRegionDrawable(new TextureRegion(texture, 0,0,1,1));\n        batch = new SpriteBatch();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void render () {\n        Gdx.gl.glClearColor(1,1,1,1);\n        Gdx.gl.glClear(GL20.GL_COLOR_BUFFER_BIT | GL20.GL_DEPTH_BUFFER_BIT);\n        batch.begin();\n        float x1 = 26.80124f;\n        float w = 586.1776f;\n        regionDrawable.draw(batch, x1, 25, w, 2); // blue line for comparison\n        tiledDrawable.draw(batch, x1, 10, w, 10); // tiled drawable, should have same length\n        batch.end();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void dispose() {\n        batch.dispose();\n        texture.dispose();\n    }\n}\n\n```\n","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/comments/91220876/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"mk1x86","id":4849383,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ4NDkzODM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4849383?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mk1x86","html_url":"https://github.com/mk1x86","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mk1x86/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mk1x86/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mk1x86/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mk1x86/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mk1x86/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mk1x86/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mk1x86/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mk1x86/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mk1x86/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/comments/91285921","html_url":"https://github.com/libgdx/libgdx/issues/3017#issuecomment-91285921","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/3017","id":91285921,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDkxMjg1OTIx","user":{"login":"NathanSweet","id":434010,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQzNDAxMA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/